 or your interest\; please consider any of our other available plantings! We
  could really use your help at any of our March 19th events!<br><br>=======
 ======</span>&nbsp\; <br><u></u><br><u></u>&nbsp\;<u></u><br><u></u>Help pl
 ant hundreds of native trees and shrubs at this site in NW Portland!<br><p>
 Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The pla
 nting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and planting guidance -
 - all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather wearing sturdy shoe
 s or boots\, and be ready to have fun!<br><br></p><p><b>Under age 18?</b>&n
 bsp\;We request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.&n
