 dsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><b>Volunteer Frequently Asked Questions webpa
 ge</b></a>&nbsp\;for more details.&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\;&nbsp\;</p
 ><p><b>Questions?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&nbsp\;<b><a href="h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Volunteer FAQ webpage</a></b>.&nb
 sp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbsp\; You can reach Gabriel\, Carey
 \, and Jenny at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><b>volu
 nteer@friendsoftrees.org</b></a>&nbsp\;We look forward to planting together
