DESCRIPTION:This planting is in conjunction with EMSWCD\, Portland Parks an
 d Recreation\, and Johnson Creek Watershed Council. Errol Heights Natural A
 rea consists of a steep-walled canyon formed by extensive natural springs f
 rom the Portland aquifer. The springs are the headwaters to Errol Heights C
 reek\, a tributary of Johnson Creek.  Friends of Trees will provide morning
  refreshments\, gloves\, tools\, and all necessary guidance. Please wear st
 urdy shoes and dress for the weather. This planting is generously sponsored
  by Portland General Electric. Please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@Friendsof
 Trees.org or 503-282-8846 x24 for more information.
