DESCRIPTION:This event is in partnership with the City of Tualatin\, the Ti
 mbers\, and Clean Water Services. We will be removing ivy from mature trees
  at this community park located along the banks of the Tualatin River.\n\nP
 lease arrive around 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a crew. The tre
 e care event will start promptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks and
  hot chocolate/coffee\, as well as gloves\, tools and guidance. Please come
  dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and get ready to have fun
 !\n\nRSVPs are kindly requested for groups of more than 5 people - click <a
  href=http://www.friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/group-registration-request-fo
 rm>HERE</a> to do so.   Please contact Jenny or Ian at (503) 595-0213 if yo
 u have any questions or need more information. \n\n
