DESCRIPTION:We will be planting trees and re-mulching previously planted tr
 ees.  We are very excited to continue reforesting the transportation corrid
 or that runs from the Columbia River in the North to the City of Gladstone 
 in the south. Metro\, ODOT\, TriMet\, EMSWCD are partnering this season wit
 h Friends of Trees to increase livability\, habitat and air quality along t
 he I-205 corridor. This planting/tree care event is generously sponsored by
  The Standard Insurance.\n\nPlease arrive around 8:45am to be registered an
 d assigned to a crew. The planting will start promptly at 9:00am. We provid
 e breakfast snacks and hot chocolate/coffee\, as well as gloves\, tools and
  guidance. Please come dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and
  get ready to have fun!\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact Andy or J
 enny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more information. 
 We look forward to seeing you out there! \n
