 ="ow3098" __is_owner="true">youth waiver</a> is required for you to volunte
 er. We ask that youth 15 years and younger are accompanied by an adult.<br>
 <br>This planting is part of Tree For All\, a partnership which has planted
  more than eight million native plants in the Tualatin River Watershed sinc
 e 2005! Clean Water Services\, Friends of Trees\, thousands of volunteers\,
