DESCRIPTION:<a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/volunteer-in-sal
 em#CrewLeader>Crew Leaders</a> are trained volunteers who are crucial to su
 ccessful Friends of Trees' events. They are trained to lead groups of volun
 teers in proper planting technique and maintain a fun and educational vibe 
 at our events.\n\nFriends of Trees is aiming to plant tens of thousands of 
 native trees and shrubs across Salem parks and green spaces this year. Help
  us make those goals a reality and register to become a crew leader with us
 ! Crew Leaders commit to guiding small groups of planters at 3-4 Saturday m
 orning plantings. \n\n<b>Sign up to attend our Salem Crew Leader training! 
 </b> Click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/2012-08-29-17-44-
 58/salem-crew-leader-training>HERE</a> to register and we'll send you more 
 information.\n\nYou may also contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 595-0213 if yo
 u have any questions or need more information. We hope to see you at traini
 ng in October!
