 r Covid-19 within 3 days of the event.&nbsp\; We <u>recommend&nbsp\;</u>eve
 ryone is fully-vaccinated\, bring and wear a face mask when working in clos
 e quarters\, and respect 6’ of physical distance. Please see our&nbsp\;<b><
 u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u>Volunteer Frequent
 ly Asked Questions webpage</u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;for more details.</p><p><b
