DESCRIPTION:<br>***************<br><br><b>This training is now full and clo
 sed</b>&nbsp\; -- thank you for your interest!&nbsp\; Please consider our o
 ther leadership positions or training for this role in Fall 2019!<br><br>**
 *************<br><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/how-to-volun
 teer/crew-leader/" target="_blank" id="ow422" __is_owner="true">Crew Leader
 s</a> are trained volunteers who lead people at our planting events to plan
 t trees correctly and have fun!&nbsp\; Friends of Trees is aiming to plant 
 tens of thousands of native trees and shrubs at more than 40 public plantin
 g events in the Green Space Program. Help make those goals a reality and re
 gister to become a Crew Leader with us!&nbsp\; After training\, we ask that
  you volunteer at 3 (or more!) planting or tree care events of your choice 
 before the end of May.<br><br>Please contact Jenny or Pablo at <a href="mai
 lto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank">volunteer@friendsoftrees.
 org</a> // (503) 595-0213 if you need more information. We look forward to 
 answering any questions you may have!
