 st snacks and hot chocolate/coffee are provided\, as well as gloves\, tools
  and guidance. Please come dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes
  and get ready to have fun!  We will be mulching native trees and shrubs th
 at were planted this past winter to increase their chance of survival throu
 gh the warm/dry summer months.\n\nThis event is in partnership with Comcast
  Cares Day.  Due to the generosity of Comcast\, there will be box lunches a
 nd tshirts provided for all volunteers!\n\n<b>RSVPs are required for this e
 vent.</b> Please RSVP <a href=https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1YFWG736LhmtG
 w7LXnkb8CjMnZBz63nOrGq9fQl4ujM4/viewform>HERE</a> to save your place at thi
 s special Earth Day event.  Exact details on where within the refuge we'll 
