 rd to seeing you out there!\n\n<i>Our partners without whom this event woul
 d not be possible include Friends of the Tualatin River National Wildlife R
 efuge\, U.S. Fish & Wildlife Service\, and Clean Water Services.  We also w
 ant to thank Comcast for their partnership in making this event a success!<
 /i>
