 e trained volunteers who are crucial to planting trees and leading small gr
 oup at our community planting events. Friends of Trees cannot run these eve
 nts without the support of this valued position!  After your training\, we 
 expect you to help lead a crew at 3 Saturday morning events Jan-April (sele
 ct for events that fit your schedule!).<br><br><i>Please note: this is an a
 ll ages venue. We will be in a private room in a separate location from the
  restaurant/brewery.<br></i><br><u>This is an In-Person training for new Cr
 ew Leaders in the Green Space program.  Please note: trainees will need to 
 have completed the online training before they attend this session</u>.  Th
 e online session will be emailed to you\, and you'll have two weeks to comp
 lete it before this in-person training.<br><br>Trainees can expect to plant
