 ive leadership skills\, and meet the staff you'll be working alongside! Lun
 ch provided\, as well as a "Tree Team" tshirt!<br><br>Questions? Please vis
 it the <a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/how-to-volunteer/crew-
