DESCRIPTION:Please note: this planting is FULL and we're not accepting grou
 p registration.  Individual volunteers are still welcome\, though!\n\nEarth
  Day!!  Come celebrate Earth Day with Friends of Trees by planting trees al
 ong the I-205 MUP in the Gateway Area. The Gateway Green is slated to be dr
 amatically transformed in the next few years. Be a part of the transformati
 on by joining us in conjunction with BES\, METRO and ODOT. This planting is
  generously sponsored by REI. Friends of Trees will provide morning refresh
 ments\, gloves\, tools\, and all necessary guidance. NOTE: This area can be
  very wet\, please wear waterproof boots and dress for the weather. \\\\n\n
 We look forward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.  Please c
 ontact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 for more in
 formation.
