 ups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunte
 ering/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for indi
 viduals or groups of 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nPlease contac
 t our Volunteer & Outreach Team at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions
  or need more information. We look forward to seeing you out there!\n\n<b>S
 pecial thanks to Portland General Electric for generously sponsoring this e
 vent.</b>
