 g/youthwaiver"><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u><
 /a></u></b>&nbsp\;signed by their parent/guardian.</p><p><b>What about Covi
 d-19?</b>&nbsp\;We&nbsp\;<u>require</u>&nbsp\;that all people at our events
  cancel if you are feeling unwell or have been exposed to someone who teste
 d positive for Covid-19 within 3 days of the event.&nbsp\; We&nbsp\;<u>reco
 mmend&nbsp\;</u>everyone is fully-vaccinated\, bring and wear a face mask w
 hen working in close quarters\, and respect 6’ of physical distance. Please
  see our&nbsp\;<b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer Frequently Asked Questions webpage</u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;for more details.&nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\; &nbsp\
 ;&nbsp\;</p><p><b>Questions?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&nbsp\;<b
