 s also happy to assist!&nbsp\; You can reach Gabriel and Jenny at&nbsp\;<b>
 <u><a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><u><u><u><u><u><u>voluntee
 r@friendsoftrees.org</u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>&nbsp\;We look forw
 ard to planting together soon!</p><b><hr></b><p>This event is in partnershi
 p with the City of Wilsonville.</p><u></u><u></u><u></u></html-blob>
