DESCRIPTION:===============================================================
 ==\n\n<b>Due to popular interest\, this planting is now FULL and closed to 
 additional group registrations.</b> We encourage you to consider our other 
 plantings happening this same day/time in Happy Valley and N Portland. \n\n
 =================================================================\n\nJoin F
 riends of Trees at the new Farmington Road Paddle Launch along the Tualatin
  River! In partnership with Tualatin Riverkeepers\, Clean Water Services\, 
 and Metro we will be planting native trees and shrubs to help revegetate po
 rtions of this soon to be completed new access point to the Tualatin. \n\nP
 lease arrive around 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a crew. The eve
 nt will start promptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks and hot choco
