 lease come dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and get ready t
 o have fun!\n\n<b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly req
 uested for groups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://www.friendso
 ftrees.org/volunteering/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not
