 store a natural area along the S Portland Riverbank at Willamette Park in P
 ortland. Please meet at the shelter at the south side of the park. Voluntee
 rs of all ages are welcome\, and no previous planting experience is necessa
 ry. Pre-registration is not required. Please wear sturdy shoes. Friends of 
