 ean Water Services as part of the ambitious Tree for All campaign.  The goa
 l of Tree for All is to plant two million trees in the Tualatin River basin
  in twenty years!  This is the second year Friends of Trees has worked at N
 yberg Creek and we are excited to build towards the goal of two million tre
 es.  This area is a wetland\, please wear rubber boots if you have them!\n\
 nPlease arrive around 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a crew. The p
 lanting will start promptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks and hot 
