 ve plants in the Tualatin River Watershed in the past decade! Clean Water S
 ervices\, Friends of Trees\, thousands of volunteers\, other non-profits\, 
 city partners\, and private landowners will be working together this season
  to continue the success of this program.\n\nPlease arrive around 8:45am to
  be registered and assigned to a crew. The planting will start promptly at 
