 loves\, tools and guidance. Please come dressed for the weather and wearing
  sturdy\, closed-toe shoes and get ready to have fun! \n\n<b>Looking to vol
 unteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for groups of more than 5
  people - click <a href=http://friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/group-regist
 ration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups 
 of 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!\n\nContact Jenny or Pablo at (503)
  595-0213 if you have any questions or need more information. \n\nWe look f
 orward to seeing you out in Tualatin!
