 not in their own household\, and follow a few other protocols\, outlined on
  our&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Volunteer
  Frequently-Aske<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u>
 </u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>d-Questions webpage</a></b>.&
