 ><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>.&nbsp\; Youth 16 and older can volunteer on t
 heir own and will need to include their parent/guardian<u></u><u></u><u></u
 ><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u><
 /u><u></u>'s contact information when they register online.<br><br><b>Quest
 ion<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u
 ></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>s?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&n
 bsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Volunteer FAQ w
 ebpage</a></b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbsp\; You can rea
 ch Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftr
 ees.org"><b>volunteer@fr<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u
 ></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u
 ><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u><
 /u><u></u><u></u><u></u>g</b></a>&nbsp\;We look forward to seeing you out t
