DESCRIPTION:<p><b>Calling all tree-planters! Your help is needed to plant h
 undreds of native trees and shrubs at Hidden Falls Natural Area! </b>Our go
 al is to enhance the upland habitat of this neighborhood gem.</p><p>Please 
 arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting s
 tarts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and planting guidance\, as wel
 l as breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate -- all you need to do is
