DESCRIPTION:Crew Leaders are trained volunteers who are crucial to plant tr
 ees properly and lead groups of volunteers at more than 80 different planti
 ng events this planting season.  Friends of Trees is aiming to plant tens o
 f thousands of native trees and shrubs at more than 40 public planting even
 ts in the Green Space Initiative Program.  Help us make those goals a reali
 ty and register to become a crew leader with us!\n\nThe training is free (a
 nd includes lunch and a t-shirt!) but registration is required.  <b>Registe
 r <a href="http://www.friendsoftrees.org/volunteering/2012-08-29-17-44-58/p
 ortland-vancouver-cl-training">HERE</a> to train for this popular role.</b>
   Spots are limited and this training will fill-up so register soon!  .\n\n
 Please contact Jenny or Ian at (503) 595-0213 if you need more information.
  We look forward to answering any questions you may have!
