DESCRIPTION:Please arrive around 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a 
 crew. The planting will start promptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snac
 ks and hot chocolate/coffee\, as well as gloves\, tools and guidance. Pleas
 e come dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and get ready to ha
 ve fun!\n\nRSVPs are kindly requested for groups of more than 5 people - cl
