DESCRIPTION:Please arrive around 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a 
 crew. The event will start promptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks 
 and hot chocolate/coffee\, as well as gloves\, tools and guidance. Please c
 ome dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and get ready to have 
 fun! \n\n<b>Looking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested
  for groups of more than 5 people - click <a href=http://www.friendsoftrees
 .org/volunteer/group-registration>HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required
