 uired for you to volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 years and younger ar
 e accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact our Volunteer &amp\; Outre
 ach Team at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more informati
 on. We look forward to seeing you out there!
