DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Earth Week by mulching hundreds of native trees and s
 hrubs that were planted this past Winter! We may also take out some weedy i
 ntroduced plants\, if time allows. <u>Note: there will be no tree-planting 
 at this event\, and this is physically-demanding work</u> (great for folks 
 looking for a work out!).  Our stewardship events help to ensure the highes
 t level of plant survival through the PNW dry summer months ahead.<u></u><b
 r><u></u><p><b>How do I register? </b>Online registration has closed at thi
 s time\, but there is still room at this event! Please simply show-up at 8:
 45am and sign-in when you arrive.</p><p><b>Please arrive by 8:45am</b> to f
 ind our tent and sign-in\, stewardship activities start promptly at 9:00am.
  We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance. All you need to do is show up dr
 essed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots (no sandals of any 
 kind\, please!) and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We req
 uest that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 an
 d older can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a <b><a href="h
 ttps://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u
 >youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></b> signed by their pare
 nt/guardian.</p><p><b>Transit:</b> B<span>us Line 155 with a .2 mile walk.<
 /span></p><p></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Pl<u></u>ease check out our <a href=
 "https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u>
 <u><u><u><u><b><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </u></u></a>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  Reach Cece and Jenny at <
 a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@fr<u></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u>g</u></b></u></
 u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a> We look forward to working together soon
 !<br></p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor <a href="https://portland
 general.com/" target="_blank"><u><u>Portland General Electric</u></u></a> &
 amp\; <a href="https://www.honltreecare.com/" target="_blank">Honl Tree Car
 e</a>.</p><p>===</p><hr /><p>This event is in partnership with City of Happ
 y Valley.</p>
