DESCRIPTION:Join Friends of Trees and the City of Happy Valley as we plant 
 native trees and shrubs to help restore the riparian vegetation around Mt. 
 Scott Creek. Mt. Scott is a tributary to Kellog Creek\, an important tribut
 ary to the Willamette River and home to Coho salmon\, Steelhead\, Pacific l
 amprey and many more wildlife species.<br><i><br></i>Please arrive around 8
 :45am to be registered and assigned to a crew. The planting will start prom
 ptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks and hot chocolate/coffee\, as w
 ell as gloves\, tools and guidance. Please come dressed for the weather and
  wearing sturdy\, closed-toe shoes and get ready to have fun! <br><br><b>Lo
 oking to volunteer as a group?</b> RSVPs are kindly requested for groups of
  more than 5 people - click <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=http%3A%2
 F%2Ffriendsoftrees.org%2Fvolunteering%2Fgroup-registration&amp\;sa=D&amp\;u
 st=1519341078934000&amp\;usg=AFQjCNEB6uaruiR9T6k7MSTwBmrFIBKzkQ" target="_b
 lank">HERE</a> to do so. RSVPs are not required for individuals or groups o
 f 4 or fewer -- you can simply show up!<br><br>Are you under age 18 and pla
 nting without your parent/guardian?  A signed <a href="https://www.google.c
 om/url?q=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.friendsoftrees.org%2Fimages%2Fstories%2Fpdf%2FYou
 th_Waiver_2015.pdf&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1519341078934000&amp\;usg=AFQjCNEpGKD
 AM-ZpdLGjms_O-b_PUBhYtQ" target="_blank">youth waiver</a> is required for y
 ou to volunteer. We kindly request youth 15 years and younger are accompani
 ed by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny or Pablo at (503) 595-0213 if y
 ou have any questions or need more information. We look forward to seeing y
 ou out there!<br><br><i>Not Accessible on Bus Line. For more directions\, v
 isit&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Ftrimet.org%2
 F&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1520451684749000&amp\;usg=AFQjCNEerSvjGRAiE7r3GFVOIEMX
 m_ngHg" target="_blank">https://trimet.org/</a>.</i><br><br>===<br>Thank yo
 u to our event sponsor\, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%
 2Fwww.portlandgeneral.com%2F&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1519341078934000&amp\;usg=A
