 y show up!\n\nPlease contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 595-0213 if you have a
 ny questions or need more information. We look forward to seeing you out th
 ere!\n\n<b>Thank you to EPSON for generously sponsoring this planting event
 .<b>\n
