 anting starts promptly at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\
 , so all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather and wearing stur
 dy shoes or boots â and be ready to have fun! <br><br><b>Under age 18?</b
 > A signed <b><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/images/stories/pdf/Youth_W
 aiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank">youth waiver</a></b> is required for you to
