 </b><br><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><b>Come out and help plant nativ
 e trees and shrubs along Gales Creek near Pacific University!</b><u></u><br
 ><u></u><br>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting c
 rew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and plantin
 g guidance -- all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather wearing
  sturdy shoes or boots\, and be ready to have fun!<u></u><br><p><b>Under ag
 e 18?</b> We request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardi
 an.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us
  a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver"><u><u><u><u><u><u>
