DESCRIPTION:Tranquil Park is a 4.5 acre green space in Wilsonville.  The Ci
 ty of Wilsonville and Friends of Trees are working to restore a healthy\, n
 ative understory and plant later-succession conifers like Hemlock and Cedar
 .  We will be planting native trees and shrubs as well as removing ivy and 
 other invasive plants from the area.\n\nPlease arrive around 8:45am to be r
 egistered and assigned to a crew. The planting will start promptly at 9:00a
 m. We provide breakfast snacks and hot chocolate/coffee\, as well as gloves
 \, tools and guidance. Please come dressed for the weather and wearing stur
 dy shoes and get ready to have fun!\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please conta
 ct Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more i
 nformation. We look forward to seeing you out there! 
