DESCRIPTION:Crew Leaders are trained volunteers who are crucial to plant tr
 ees properly and lead groups of volunteers at more than 80 different planti
 ng events this planting season.  Friends of Trees is aiming to plant tens o
 f thousands of native trees and shrubs at more than 40 public planting even
 ts in the Green Space Program.  Help us make those goals a reality and regi
 ster to become a crew leader with us!\n\nThe training is free (and includes
  lunch and a t-shirt!) but registration is required.  <b>Register <a href="
 https://docs.google.com/a/friendsoftrees.org/forms/d/1qK5n4pqfzT_OtodhgCXj9
 HzzCcPmHMB3l2_UDuzGRIg/closedform">HERE</a> to train for this popular role.
 </b>  Spots are limited and this training will fill-up so register soon!\n\
 nPlease contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 595-0213 if you need more informati
 on. We look forward to answering any questions you may have!
