DESCRIPTION:===================<br><br>Due to popular interest\, this event
  is now <b>FULL and CLOSED</b> to further volunteers.&nbsp\; Thank you for 
 understanding\, our Spring events often do fill-up.&nbsp\; Please consider 
 any of our other open planting or tree care events!<br><br>================
 ===<br><br>Friends of Trees is working with Clean Water Services and the Ja
 ckson School HOA to restore this natural area to a diverse and healthy fore
 st.&nbsp\; Join the fun and help plant hundreds of native trees and shrubs 
 -- your help is what makes this community planting possible!<br><br>Please 
