 g-with-covid-19.aspx">"Ext<u></u>reme Risk" by the State of Oregon</a>.&nbs
 p\; For all these reasons\, we feel it is irresponsible to gather a group o
 f people\, even outdoors with proper safety protocol.&nbsp\;<br><br>=====<u
 ></u>============&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<br><br>Your help is needed to plant trees a
 t this important transit center in North Portland. Friends of Trees is part
 nering with TriMet to increase tree canopy at their transit centers through
 out the Portland Metro area. This planting is possible with the support of 
 East Multnomah Soil &amp\; Water Conservation District.<br><b><br></b><b>Re
