 eir parent/guardian.<br></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <b><
 u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also happ
 y to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@fri
 endsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b>
 <u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213.  We look forward to planting together 
 soon!</p><hr /><p><b></b></p><p>This event is in partnership with the City 
 of Hillsboro.</p>
