 volunteer/how-to-volunteer/crew-leader/">Learn more and register here</a></
 b>&nbsp\;for this important position. Space limited.<br><br>This is the han
 ds-on training for new Crew Leaders in the Green Space program.&nbsp\; Trai
 nees can expect to plant different root stocks\, learn about tree identific
 ation\, and meet other Crew Leaders and staff!<br><br>Trainees will need to
  have completed an online 1.5 hr training before they attend this hands-on 
 session.&nbsp\; The online training will be open Jan 14th-28th and you can 
 complete it from the comfort of your own home.<br><p><b>What about Covid-19
 ?</b>&nbsp\;The safety of volunteers and staff is our number one priority a
 t Friends of Trees. We are requiring that all people at our events are full
