  planting has been canceled.</b>&nbsp\; Covid-19 transmission still remains
  a concern for our staff and planting partners.&nbsp\; Out of an abundance 
 of caution\, we will not be gathering a group from the public to plant at t
 his event.&nbsp\; We apologize to everyone who has signed up for this incon
 venience\, and hope to plant with you when it’s a little safer!<br><br>====
 ===========<u></u><u></u><u></u>==<br><br><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbsp\
 ;The safety of volunteers and staff is our number one priority at Friends o
 f Trees. We are requiring that all people at our events bring and wear a fa
 bric face mask\, respect 6' or more of distance from others not in their ow
 n household\, and follow a few other protocols\, outlined on our&nbsp\;<b><
 a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Volunteer Frequently-Ask
 ed-Questions webpage</a></b>.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>Under age 18?</b>&nbsp\;We r
 equest that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.&nbsp\; You
 th 16 and older can volunteer on their own and will need to include their p
 arent/guardian's contact information when they register online.<br><br>Frie
 nds of Trees in partnership with the City of Salem is undertaking a multi-y
 ear effort at McKay to help reduce weedy vegetation and establish a tree ca
 nopy to provide more shade and wildlife habitat within the wetland area of 
 the park.<br><br><b>Questions?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&nbsp\;
 <b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Volunteer FAQ webpag
 e</a></b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbsp\; You can reach Je
 nny\, Pablo\, and Carey at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.o
 rg">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a>&nbsp\;We look forward to seeing you ou
 t there!<br><br><i>Friends of Trees continues to follow the guidelines and 
 recommendations made by the CDC and Oregon Health Authority. If at any poin
 t we feel it is not safe to host events\, we will cancel them and notify an
 y volunteers who are pre-registered.</i>
