DESCRIPTION:Crew Leaders are trained volunteers who are crucial to successf
 ul Friends of Trees' events. They are trained to lead groups of volunteers 
 in proper planting technique and maintain a fun and educational vibe at our
  events.<br><br>Friends of Trees is aiming to plant thousands of native tre
 es and shrubs across Salem parks and green spaces this year. Help us make t
 hose goals a reality and register to become a Crew Leader! Crew Leaders com
 mit to guiding small groups of planters at 4 (or more) Saturday morning pla
 ntings\, Nov - April.<br><br>The training is free (and includes lunch and a
  t-shirt!) but registration is required.&nbsp\; Register&nbsp\;<a href="htt
 p://friendsoftrees.org/salem-crew-leader-training/" target="_blank">HERE</a
 > to train for this popular role.&nbsp\; Spots are limited and this trainin
 g will fill-up so <a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/salem-crew-leader-trai
 ning/" target="_blank">register now!</a><br><br>You may also contact Jenny 
 or Pablo at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more informati
 on. We hope to see you at the training!
