 vent on this same day at the <strong>Tualatin River Greenway (7041 SW Nyber
 g St\, Tualatin\, OR 97062)</strong>. Information about this event is also 
 included in the calendar above.\n\nPlease contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 5
 95-0213 if you have any questions or need more information. We look forward
  to seeing you out there!\n\n<b>Special thanks to the NW Natural for genero
 usly sponsoring this event.</b>
