 and shrubs as well.\n\n<strong>Due to great interest in this event\, sign-u
 ps for groups are now closed.</strong> If you are still hoping to plant wit
 h us\, <strong>please consider heading to the Durham City Park planting</st
 rong> - it's just 15 minute drive south of Hall Creek\, and needs some extr
 a support! Information about the Durham planting can be found on the calend
 ar listing above.\n\nPlease contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 595-0213 if you
  have any questions or need more information.\n\nThese Hall Creek plantings
  are in partnership with the City of Beaverton and Clean Water Services and
  supported by a Metro voter-approved Nature in Neighborhoods grant.\n
