 nder age 18? </u></b>A signed <a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/images/sto
 ries/pdf/Youth_Waiver_2015.pdf" target="_blank">youth waiver</a> is require
 d for you to volunteer. We ask that youth 15 years and younger are accompan
 ied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at (503) 5
 95-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank">vo
 lunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a> if you have questions or need any further in
 formation. We look forward to seeing you out there!<br><br><i>Accessible on
  Bus Line 87. For more directions\, visit&nbsp\;<a href="https://trimet.org
 /" target="_blank">https://trimet.org/</a>.</i>
