 ees properly and lead groups of volunteers at more than 65 different planti
 ng events this planting season.  Friends of Trees is aiming to plant over 2
 5\,000 street and yard trees in our Green Space Initiative program.  Help u
 s make those goals a reality!  Pre-registration for this training is requir
 ed.  To sign up\, please visit this page:  http://www.friendsoftrees.org/vo
 lunteer/trainings/gsi-cl-training
