 d wear a face mask when working in close quarters\, and respect 6’ of physi
 cal distance. Please see our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volu
 nteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer Frequently 
