DESCRIPTION:The Rock Creek Partnership will be celebrating the second annua
 l Watershed Wide Event on March 16th.  Volunteers will work sites to remove
  invasive weeds and plant native trees at streamside areas across the water
 shed. This streamside restoration work improves the quality of water that f
 lows into the Clackamas River and creates healthy habitats for fish and wil
 dlife. Gloves\, tools\, and all necessary guidance will be provided. Please
  wear sturdy shoes and dress for the weather.\n\nThis project is supported 
 with funding from Clackamas County Water Environment Services\, on behalf o
 f Clackamas Service District No. 1.
