DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Earth Week by mulching hundreds of native trees and s
 hrubs that were planted this past winter! We may also take out some weedy i
 ntroduced plants\, if time allows. <u>Note: there will be no tree-planting 
 at this event\, and this is physically-demanding work</u> (great for folks 
 looking for a work out!).  Our stewardship events help to ensure the highes
 t level of plant survival through the PNW dry summer months ahead.<b><br></
 b><br><b>How do I register?</b> Online registration has closed at this time
 \, but there is still room at this event!  Please simply show-up and sign i
 n when you arrive!<br><p><b>Please arrive by 8:45am</b> to find our tent an
 d sign-in\, stewardship activities start promptly at 9:00am. We provide glo
 ves\, tools\, and guidance. All you need to do is show up dressed for the w
 eather and wearing sturdy shoes or boots (no sandals of any kind\, please!)
  and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that youth
  15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can vol
 unteer on their own and will need to hand us a <b><a href="https://friendso
 ftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth
  waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></b> signed by thei
 r parent/guardian.</p><p></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Pl<u></u>ease check out 
 our <a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u>
 <u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></b></u></u
 ></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.  Our team is also happy to a
 ssist!  Reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.or
 g" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@fr<u
 ></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u>g</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></a> We look forward to working together soon!<br></p><p>===<br>Th
 ank you to our event sponsors <a href="https://portlandgeneral.com/" target
 ="_blank"><u><u><u>Portland General Electric</u></u></u></a> &amp\; <a href
 ="https://www.honltreecare.com/" target="_blank">Honl Tree Care</a>.</p><p>
 ===</p><hr /><p>This event is in partnership with City of Wilsonville\, fun
