DESCRIPTION:Crew leaders will guide groups of volunteer planters as they re
 store a natural area at MacGregor Heights in Portland. Volunteers of all ag
 es are welcome\, and no previous planting experience is necessary. Pre-regi
 stration is not required. Please wear sturdy shoes and appropriate attire (
 rain gear and warm layers). Friends of Trees will have native trees and pla
 nts\, gloves and tools at the site. Please contact Greg Tudor if you have q
 uestions or if you know in advance that you will be able to attend: gregt@f
 riendsoftrees.org or 503-282-8846 ext. 12.\n\nThis planting is proudly spon
 sored by REI.
