DESCRIPTION:Please note: this planting is FULL and we're not accepting grou
 p registration.  Individual volunteers are still welcome\, though!\n\nWe ar
 e very happy to continue our partnership with the City of Hillsboro and Cle
 an Water Services. This is part of the Tree for All Campaign\, CWS' ambitio
 us plan to plant 2 million trees in the Tualatin River Basin! This is Frien
 ds of Trees first time at this site\, which is near Rock Creek\, a tributar
 y to the Tualatin River and home to both of our native turtle species! Frie
 nds of Trees will provide morning refreshments\, gloves\, tools\, and all n
 ecessary guidance. Please wear sturdy shoes and dress for the weather. \n\n
 We look forward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.  Please c
 ontact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 for more in
 formation.
