 an><span><span><span><br></span></span></span></span></span></span><br><br>
 ==========<br><span><span><span><span><span><span><br></span></span></span>
 </span></span></span><br><span><span><span><span><span><span>Join Friends o
 f Trees and the City of Salem to enhance riparian corridors at this popular
  park in W Salem! The trees and shrubs we plant will provide valuable shade
  to the creek and stabilize the banks. Your support is crucial to the succe
 ss of this project -- thank you for considering signing-up!</span></span></
 span></span></span></span><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assi
 gned a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, to
 ols\, and planting guidance\, as well as breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/ho
