DESCRIPTION:===============================================================
 ===<br><br>Pre-registration for this event has closed\, but this planting i
 s still open to more volunteers.&nbsp\; Please simply show up and sign-in w
 hen you arrive!<br><br>====================================================
 ==============<br><br>Kick off the new year by planting trees and help Chur
 chill Forest natural area become a diverse and healthy riparian forest and 
 wetland area! This planting project is situated in the headwaters of Summer
  Creek and will help to protect the uppermost section of the watershed by p
 lanting a wide variety of native trees and shrubs. We couldn't do it withou
 t your support -- thank you for considering signing-up!&nbsp\;<br><br>Pleas
 e arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and enjoy some breakfast treats and coffee\, 
 tea\, or hot chocolate. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, 
