DESCRIPTION:<b>Registration for this Crew Leader Training in Salem is close
 d. Thank you for your interest! </b><br><b><br></b><br>=================<br
 ><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/how-to-volunteer/crew-leader
 /" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u>Planting C</u></u></u></u></u></a><a href
 ="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/how-to-volunteer/crew-leader/" targe
 t="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u>rew Leaders</u></u></u></u></u></a> are trained v
 olunteers who are crucial to planting trees and leading small group at our 
 community planting events. Friends of Trees cannot run these events without
  the support of this valued position!  After your training\, we expect you 
 to help lead a crew at 4 Saturday morning events Nov-April (select for even
 ts that fit your schedule!).    <br><br><u>This is the Salem In-Person trai
 ning for new Crew Leaders in program.  Please note: trainees will need to h
 ave completed the online training before they attend this session</u>.  The
  online session will be sent to you and available for two weeks.<br><br>===
