 n Gales Creek since 2016. Your support is crucial to the success of this pr
 oject -- thank you for considering signing-up!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45a
 m to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am
 . We provide gloves\, tools\, and planting guidance\, as well as breakfast 
