 u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.  Our team is also happy to 
 assist! <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@fr<u></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u>
 g</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a> / 503-595-0213 We
  look forward to working together soon!<br></p><b><hr /></b><p>This event i
 n partnership with Clean Water Services.<br></p>
