 perennial plants at the 7th and Sandy Green Street Project in partnership w
 ith Depave!  Activities will include planting <span>into a variety of creat
 ive\, plantable urban objects.  </span><span>This project is combining traf
 fic calming\, placemaking\, and green infrastructure at an over-paved inter
 section of Central Eastside Portland -- join the fun and make a difference!
 </span></p><p><b>How do I register? </b><span>Fill out </span><b><a href="h
 ttps://www.tfaforms.com/4840511?tfa_26=a0T5G00000P1V8P&tfa_2189=7th%20and%2
