DESCRIPTION:<p>=======</p><p><b>Due to popular interest\, this event is now
  <u>full and closed</u></b>.  Please consider any of our open events -- we 
 hope to work with you soon!</p><p>=======</p><p><span>Calling all tree plan
 ters! Invite your friends and family\, and join the fun at West Bethany Cre
 ek in Bethany! The goal of this event is to plant hundreds of native trees 
 and shrubs in order to improve the riparian buffer surrounding the creek. <
 /span></p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting 
 crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and planti
 ng guidance\, as well as breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate -- a
 ll you need to do is show up dressed for the weather wearing sturdy shoes o
 r boots\, and be ready to have fun!<br></p><p><b>Under age 18?</b><span> We
  request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 1
 6 and older can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a </span><b
 ><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><
 u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b><span> signed by t
 heir parent/guardian.</span></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our 
 <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><
 u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our t
 eam is also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mail
 to:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><b><u>voluntee
 r@friendsoftrees.org</u></b></u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213.  We look f
 orward to planting together soon!</p><p>===</p><p>Thank you to our event sp
 onsors <a href="https://www.laika.com/">Laika</a>\, <a href="https://www.ha
 mptonlumber.com/" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Hampton 
 Lumber</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a> &amp\; <a href="http
 s://portlandgeneral.com/" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>Portland Genera
 l Electric</u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.</p><p>===</p><b><hr /></b><p>This e
 vent is in partnership with the Clean Water Services.</p>
