DESCRIPTION:<br>===============<u></u>======<br><br><b>Due to the large nat
 ure of this event\, and recommendations from our local health officials to 
 avoid spreading the Coronavirus\, <u>this event is now cancelled</u>.</b>&n
 bsp\; We apologize for this and ask for your understanding as we try to do 
 what's best for our community's health!<br><br>========<u></u>=============
 &nbsp\;&nbsp\;<br><br>This is our final community planting at this incredib
 le site for the planting season.&nbsp\; We hope you'll join in the effort t
 o plant many hundreds of native trees and shrubs and green this well-loved 
 natural area in the beautiful Columbia River Gorge!<br><br>Friends of Trees
  is partnering with the Sandy River Watershed Council and Friends of the Sa
 ndy River Delta with support from the US Forest Service\, Ash Creek Forestr
 y Management\, Daimler Trucks\, the Portland Trailblazers\, the Nature Cons
 ervancy\, and the Boeing Company to continue restoring the Sandy River Delt
 a.<br><br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at (503) 595-0213 //
  <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org
 </a> if you have questions or need any further information. We look forward
  to seeing you out there!<br><br>============<br><br>Esta es nuestra planta
 ción comunitaria final en este increíble sitio para la temporada de plantac
 ión. ¡Esperamos que se una al esfuerzo por plantar cientos de árboles y arb
 ustos nativos y ecologizar este parque tan querido en la hermosa río del Co
 lumbia!<br><br><br><br>Friends of Trees se ha asociado con Sandy River Wate
 rshed Council y Friends of the Sandy River Delta con el apoyo del Servicio 
 Forestal de EE. UU.\, Ash Creek Forestry Management\, Daimler Trucks\, Port
 land Trailblazers\, Nature Conservancy y Boeing Company para continuar esta
  restauración proceso en el delta del río Sandy<br><br>Comuníquese con Jenn
 y\, Pablo o Carey al (503) 595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoft
 rees.org">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a> si tiene preguntas o necesita má
 s información. ¡Esperamos verte por ahí!<br><br>===<br>Thank you to our eve
 nt sponsors <a href="https://www.nba.com/blazers/">Trail Blazers</a>\, <a h
 ref="https://daimler-trucksnorthamerica.com/">Daimler Trucks North America<
 /a>\, <a href="https://www.elemental.com/">AWS Elemental</a>!<br>===&nbsp\;
 &nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;
