 orest Park sites are small and located in sensitive habitat\, so we need to
  limit how many people can participate.  <b>Please <a href=https://docs.goo
 gle.com/a/friendsoftrees.org/spreadsheet/viewform?usp=drive_web&formkey=dGh
 1cmpyQlZKeDhlTVFJbDdXclFwdEE6MA#gid=0>REGISTER HERE</a> to volunteer at thi
 s event and we'll send you the address and other event details!</b>\n\nPlea
 se arrive 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a crew. The event will st
 art promptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks and hot chocolate/coffe
 e\, as well as gloves\, tools and guidance. Please come dressed for the wea
 ther and wearing sturdy shoes or boots and get ready to have fun!\n\nPlease
  contact Jenny or Ian at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need m
 ore information.\n\n<i>This event is generously sponsored by <b>REI</b>.</I
 >\n\n\n
