 u></a></u></b> signed by their parent/guardian.</p><p><b>What about Covid-1
 9?</b> We <u>require</u> that all people at our events cancel if you are fe
 eling unwell or have been exposed to someone who tested positive for Covid-
 19 within 3 days of the event.  We <u>recommend </u>everyone is fully-vacci
 nated\, bring and wear a face mask when working in close quarters\, and res
 pect 6’ of physical distance. Please see our <b><u><a href="https://friends
 oftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Voluntee
 r Frequently Asked Questions webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></u></a></u></b> for more details.        </p><p><b>Questions?  </
 b>Please check out our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-
 faq/"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also 
