DESCRIPTION:Please join Friends of Trees in partnership with Portland Parks
  & Recreation during Forest Park Conservancy's Day of Stewardship to plant 
 native trees and shrubs in Forest Park. We have been removing English Ivy f
 rom an area of Forest Park and it is now ready for planting!\n\n<b>Due to a
  great response\, this event is now closed to further sign-ups.</b> If you 
 are seeking other opportunities to volunteer on Saturday\, October 17th\, p
 lease consider joining us at our Murrayhill planting in Beaverton\, focusin
 g on watershed restoration!\n\nPlease contact Jenny or Randi at (503) 595-0
 213 if you have any questions or need more information.\n\n<i>This planting
  is generously supported by <b>REI</b>.</I>
