 u><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></
 a></u></b> signed by their parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please
  check out our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" ta
 rget="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  Yo
 u can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"
  target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org
 </u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forwar
 d to planting together soon!</p><b><hr /></b><p>This event in partnership w
 ith Clean Water Services.<br></p>
