DESCRIPTION:<p>Help needed to plant hundreds of native trees\, shrubs\, and
  wildflowers along Fanno Creek Greenway! This is a 3 acre parcel of land al
 ong Fanno Creek\, which is an amazing and unique urban stream that begins i
 n Portland’s SW hills and meanders 15 miles through neighborhoods in Portla
 nd\, Beaverton\, Tigard and Durham.  Let's take care of our trees and water
 ways so they can take care of us!</p><p>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in 
 and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide 
 gloves\, tools\, and planting guidance\, as well as breakfast snacks and co
 ffee/tea/hot chocolate -- all you need to do is show up dressed for the wea
 ther wearing sturdy shoes or boots\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p><b>How
  do I register? </b><span>Online pre-registration has closed at this time\,
  but there is still room at this event! Please simply show up at 8:45am\, a
 nd sign-in when you arrive. Please note that there is limited street parkin
 g in the immediate area\, DO NOT park at operating business parking lots. <
 /span></p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that youth 15 and under volunt
 eer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own 
 and will need to hand us a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwa
 iver" target="_blank"><u>youth waiver form</u></a></u></b> signed by their 
 parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Transit:</b> Bus L<span>ine 56 with a .3 mile wal
 k.</span></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <b><u><a href="http
 s://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u>Volunteer FAQ web
 page</u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  You can reach Cec
 e and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank
 "><b><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></b></a>\, 503-595-0213.  We look f
 orward to planting together soon!</p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event spons
 or <a href="https://portlandgeneral.com/" target="_blank">Portland General 
 Electric</a> &amp\; <a href="https://www.hamptonlumber.com/" target="_blank
 "><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Hampton Lumber</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.</p><
 p>===</p><b><hr /></b><p>This event is in partnership with the City of Beav
 erton.<br></p>
