DESCRIPTION:<b>=======</b><br><br><b>Due to popular interest\, this event i
 s <u>full and closed</u>.</b> Please consider any of other open event -- we
  hope to work with you soon!<br><br><b>=======</b><br><b><br></b><u></u><u>
 </u><u></u><u></u><b>Calling all tree planters for your help to plant hundr
 eds of native trees and shrubs along Saum Creek Trail in Tualatin!</b> Saum
  Creek Trail runs along Saum Creek\, a tributary of the nearby Tualatin Riv
 er. <br><br>Please arrive by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting c
 rew. The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and plantin
 g guidance\, as well as breakfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate -- al
 l you need to do is show up dressed for the weather wearing sturdy shoes or
  boots\, and be ready to have fun!<b><br></b><br><u></u><u></u><b>Under age
  18?</b> We request that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardia
 n.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us 
 a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver"><u><u><u><u><u><u><
 u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by their parent/guardian.<p><b>Wha
 t about Covid-19?</b> We <u>require</u> that all people at our events cance
 l if you are feeling unwell or have been exposed to someone who tested posi
 tive for Covid-19 within 3 days of the event.  We <u>recommend </u>everyone
  is fully-vaccinated\, bring and wear a face mask when working in close qua
 rters\, and respect 6’ of physical distance. Please see our <b><u><a href="
 https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u
 ><u><u><u>Volunteer Frequently Asked Questions webpage</u></u></u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> for more details.        </
 p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <b><u><a href="https://friends
 oftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volun
 teer FAQ webpage</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a
 ></u></b>.  Our team is also happy to assist!  You can reach Gabriel and Je
 nny at <b><u><a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><u><u><u><u><u><
 u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></u></u></u></u><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> We look forward to planting
  together soon!</p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor <a href="https:
 //oregonsoapcompany.com/"><u><u>Oregon Soap Company</u></u></a>.<br>===<br>
 </p><b><hr /></b><p>This event is in partnership with the City of Tualatin.
 <br></p><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>
