DESCRIPTION:Do you want a few more native plants to add to your landscape? 
  Then please join us for a native tree and shrub giveaway at our Spring Mou
 ntain site (made possible by funding from the Arbor Day Foundation).<br><ul
 ><li>Each household is able to receive up to 4 native trees and/or shrubs. 
 All species are 1-gallon container stock.</li><li>This giveaway is focused 
 on Clackamas County residents\, though all are welcome. </li><li>Trees and 
 shrubs will be available on a first-come\, first-served basis. </li></ul><b
 r><u>Plant list includes</u>: Black Hawthorn\, Black Twinberry\, Douglas Fi
 r\, Mock Orange\, Tall Oregon Grape\, Ocean Spray\, Osoberry\, Pacific Crab
  Apple\, Pacific Ninebark\, Ponderosa Pine\, Red Elderberry\, Red0flowering
  Currant\, Red Osier Dogwood\, Salmonberry\, Vine Maple\, Western Servicebe
 rry\, and Western Spirea.<br>We hope to see you there!
