DESCRIPTION:We are partnering with Portland Parks & Recreation and Forest P
 ark Conservancy to remove English Ivy from this area of Forest Park\, in pr
 eparation for a future native tree and shrub planting.\n\nThis event is now
  full -- thank you for your interest!  Due to the size and sensitivity of t
 he site we need to limit the number of participants.  Thank you for your un
 derstanding -- we hope to work in Forest Park with you in the future!\n\nPl
 ease contact Jenny or Ian at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or ne
 ed more information.\n\n<i>This planting is generously sponsored by Whole F
 oods.</i>\n\n\n
