DESCRIPTION:<br>=================<br><br><b>Due to popular interest\, this 
 event is now <u>full and closed</u>.&nbsp\;</b> Please consider any of our 
 future events that remain open - we hope to plant with you soon!<br><br>===
 ==============<br>Let's plant hundreds of native seedlings together at a re
 markable natural area\, the Sandy River Delta!&nbsp\; &nbsp\;<b><br></b><br
 ><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbsp\;The safety of volunteers and staff is ou
 r number one priority at Friends of Trees. We are requiring that all people
  at our events bring and wear a fabric face mask\, respect 6' or more of di
 stance from others not in their own household\,bringing your own water bott
 le and any other snacks or beverages you will need\, and follow a few other
  protocols\, outlined on our&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/v
 olunteer-faq/">Volunteer Frequently-Asked-Questions webpage</a></b>.&nbsp\;
 <br><br><b>Under age 18?</b>&nbsp\;We request that youth 15 and under volun
 teer with a parent/guardian.&nbsp\; Youth 16 and older can volunteer on the
 ir own and will need to include their parent/guardian's contact information
  when they register online.<br><br>This event is in partnership with the Sa
 ndy River Watershed Council and Friends of the Sandy River Delta with suppo
 rt from the US Forest Service\, Ash Creek Forestry Management\, Daimler Tru
 cks\, the Portland Trailblazers\, the Nature Conservancy\, and the Boeing C
 ompany.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<b><br></b><br><b>Questions?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please c
 heck out our&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">V
 olunteer FAQ webpage</a></b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbsp
 \; You can reach Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:Volunte
 er@friendsoftrees.org"><b>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</b></a>&nbsp\;We loo
 k forward to seeing you out there!&nbsp\; &nbsp\;<br><br><i>Friends of Tree
 s continues to follow the guidelines and recommendations made by the CDC an
 d Oregon Health Authority. If at any point we feel it is not safe to host e
 vents\, we will cancel them and notify any volunteers who are pre-registere
 d.</i><br><i><br></i><br><br>===<br>Thank you to our sponsors <a href="http
 s://daimler-trucksnorthamerica.com/" id="ow10009" __is_owner="true">Daimler
  Trucks North America</a>&nbsp\;&amp\;&nbsp\;<a href="https://www.nba.com/b
 lazers/" id="ow10005" __is_owner="true">Portland Trailblazers</a>!<br>===&n
 bsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\;<i><br></i>
