DESCRIPTION:<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer/how-to-volunte
 er/crew-leader/">Crew Leaders</a></b> are trained volunteers who are crucia
 l to successful Friends of Trees' events. They are trained to lead groups o
 f volunteers in proper planting technique and maintain a fun and educationa
 l vibe at our events.<br><br>Your help is needed to plant thousands of nati
 ve trees and shrubs across Salem parks and green spaces this year. Let's do
  this together!&nbsp\; Make those goals a reality and register to become a 
 Crew Leader. Crew Leaders commit to guiding small groups of planters at 4 (
 or more) Saturday morning plantings\, Nov - April.<br><br>Contact Jenny or 
 Pablo at 503-595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org">volu
 nteer@friendsoftrees.org</a> if you have any questions or need more informa
 tion. We hope to see you at the training!
