 ater this season and hope that you'll keep in touch to help us plant them a
 t a later date!<br><br>===============</span>&nbsp\;</p><p>Let's plant tree
 s together in NE Salem! Dozens of large (6-10' tall) trees will be ready fo
 r planting in their new homes\, and your help is what makes this community 
