 rees.org/youthwaiver">youth waiver form</a></b>&nbsp\;signed by their paren
 t/guardian.</p><p><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbsp\;The safety of volunteer
 s and staff is our number one priority at Friends of Trees. We are requirin
 g that all people at our events are fully-vaccinated (with the exception of
