 severely immunocompromised\, etc)<b>\,</b>&nbsp\;bring and wear a face mask
  through the event introductions\, respect 6' or more of distance from othe
 rs not in their own household\, bring your own water bottle and any other s
 nacks or beverages you will need\, and cancel if anyone in your household f
