DESCRIPTION:<span><span>================<br><br>This event is now <b><u>ful
 l and closed</u></b>.&nbsp\; Thank you for your interest\, we hope you cons
 ider our December 11th event at McKay Park or another <a href="https://frie
 ndsoftrees.org/salem/">Salem-area event</a> this season!<br><br>===========
 =====</span></span><p><b>Under age 18?</b>&nbsp\;We request that youth 15 a
 nd under volunteer with a parent/guardian.&nbsp\; Youth 16 and older can vo
 lunteer on their own and will need to hand us a&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://f
 riendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver">youth waiver form</a></b>&nbsp\;signed by th
 eir parent/guardian.</p><p><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbsp\;The safety of 
 volunteers and staff is our number one priority at Friends of Trees. We are
  requiring that all people at our events are fully-vaccinated (with the exc
 eption of those younger than 12 and anyone&nbsp\;severely immunocompromised
  and not eligible for the vaccine)<b>\,</b>&nbsp\;bring and wear a face mas
 k through the event introductions\, respect 6' or more of distance from oth
 ers not in their own household\, bring your own water bottle and any other 
 snacks or beverages you will need\, and cancel if anyone in your household 
 feels unwell within two weeks of this event. Please see our&nbsp\;<a href="
 https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><b>Volunteer Frequently Asked Qu
 estions webpage</b></a>&nbsp\;for more details.</p><p><b>Questions?&nbsp\;&
 nbsp\;</b>Please check out our&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org
 /volunteer-faq/">Volunteer FAQ webpage</a></b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also hap
 py to assist!&nbsp\; You can reach Jenny and Carey at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto
 :Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><b>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</b></a>&nbsp
 \;Welook forward to planting together soon!</p><b><hr></b><br>This event is
  supported by the City of Salem.<br><br><i>Friends of Trees continues to fo
 llow the guidelines and recommendations made by the CDC and Oregon Health A
 uthority. If at any point we feel it is not safe to host events\, we will c
 ancel them and notify any volunteers who are pre-registered.</i>
