 s and help increase the water quality and habitat value in this "hidden gem
 " of NE Portland.  We will be mulching native trees and shrubs planted in J
 anuary and March.  We may also be doing some invasive species removal.\n\nP
 lease arrive around 8:45am to be registered and assigned to a crew. The tre
