 ader/">rew Leaders</a>&nbsp\;are trained volunteers who are crucial to plan
 ting trees and leading small group at our community planting events. Friend
 s of Trees can not run these events without the support of this valued posi
 tion! This training is for mid-Willamette Valley residents who are interest
 ed in the Crew Leader role at our upcoming Salem\, OR planting events!<br><
 br><b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/salem/">Learn more and register h
 ere</a></b>&nbsp\;for this important position. Space limited.<br><b><p></p>
 </b><ul><li><b><u>What about Covid-19?</u></b>&nbsp\;We are requiring that 
 all volunteers and staff are fully-vaccinated\, arrive at all events wearin
 g a face masks (depending on the event it may be possible to remove your ma
 sk after planting begins)\, and maintain 6' or more of physical space from 
 folks outside of your household. We'll explain more at the training\, but a
 lso feel free to check out our&nbsp\;<a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/vo
 lunteer-faq/">Covid-19 &amp\; Volunteer FAQ page</a>&nbsp\;for more details
 .</li></ul><ul><li><b><u>A note on planting location and personal transport
 ation</u>:</b>&nbsp\;You will be eligible to Crew Lead at plantings events 
