  Due to Covid-19\, personal transportation is highly recommended-- we canno
 t guarantee that carpools will be available due to differing comfort levels
  of other FOT volunteers.</li></ul><b><p></p><hr><p></p></b>Ple<u></u>ase c
 ontact Jenny or Carey if you need more information or have questions:&nbsp\
 ;<a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org">volunteer@frien<u></u>dsoftr
 ees.org</a>. We look forward to working with you this planting season!
