  trees and shrubs planted in December and early April.  We may also be digg
 ing out some Himalayan blackberry roots.    \n\nPlease arrive around 8:45am
  to be registered and assigned to a crew. The tree care event will start pr
 omptly at 9:00am. We provide breakfast snacks and hot chocolate/coffee\, as
  well as gloves\, tools and guidance. Please come dressed for the weather a
 nd wearing sturdy shoes and get ready to have fun!\n\nRSVPs are not require
 d. Please contact Andy or Jenny at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions
  or need more information. We look forward to seeing you out there!\n
