 ur Spring Tree Care events!&nbsp\; Please consider any of the other open gr
 een 'Tree Care' events in May.</p><p>===========<wbr><u></u>===</p><br>Your
  help is needed to mulch hundreds of native trees and shrubs that were plan
 ted this past winter at this natural area site just East of the PDX airport
 ! We may also take out some weedy introduced plants\, if time allows.&nbsp\
 ;<u>Note: there will be no tree-planting at this event\, and this is physic
 ally-demanding work</u>&nbsp\;(great for folks looking for a work out!).&nb
 sp\; Our Tree Care events help to ensure the highest level of plant surviva
 l through the PNW dry summer months ahead.<br><br><b>Please arrive by 9:45a
 m</b>&nbsp\;to find our tent and sign-in\, Tree Care activities start promp
 tly at 10:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and guidance\, so all you need 
