 ><br>=================</span></span><br><br><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbs
 p\;The safety of volunteers and staff is our number one priority at Friends
  of Trees. We are requiring that all people at our events bring and wear a 
 fabric face mask\, respect 6' or more of distance from others not in their 
 own household\,bringing your own water bottle and any other snacks or bever
 ages you will need\,&nbsp\;and follow a few other protocols\, outlined on o
 ur&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">Volunteer F
