 arm layers). Friends of Trees will have native trees and plants\, gloves an
 d tools at the site.\n\nPlease contact Greg Tudor if you have questions or 
 if you know in advance that you will be able to attend: gregt@friendsoftree
 s.org or 503-282-8846 ext. 12.
