 u></u>.&nbsp\; Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own and will need 
 to include their parent/guardian<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><
 u></u>'s contact information when they register online.<br><br><b>Question<
 u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>s?&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</b>Please 
 check out our&nbsp\;<b><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/">
 Volunteer FAQ webpage</a></b>.&nbsp\; Our team is also happy to assist!&nbs
 p\; You can reach Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at&nbsp\;<a href="mailto:Volunt
 eer@friendsoftrees.org"><b>volunteer@fr<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><
 u></u><u></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></
 u>g</b></a>&nbsp\;We look forward to seeing you out there!<br><br><i>Friend
 s of Trees continues to follow the guidelines and recommendations made by t
 he CDC and Oregon Health Authority. If at any point we feel it is not safe 
