  are also partnering with us to  plant native trees and shrubs to help rest
 ore the Johnson Creek Watershed's native habitats\, increase water quality 
 and reduce the amount of stormwater entering the creek. Friends of Trees wi
 ll provide morning refreshments\, gloves\, tools\, and all necessary guidan
 ce. Please wear sturdy shoes and dress for the weather. \n\nWe look forward
  to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not required.  Please contact Andy Mee
 ks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0213 for more information.
