 r with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their own an
 d will need to hand us a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiv
 er" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth waiv
 er form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u>
 </b> signed by their parent/guardian.<br></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please c
 heck out our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" targ
 et="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webp
 age</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>
 .  Our team is also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a hr
 ef="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u>
