  this event is now <u>full and closed</u>.&nbsp\;</b> Please consider any o
 f our future events that remain open - we hope to plant with you soon!<br><
 br>=================</span><br><br><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbsp\;The sa
 fety of volunteers and staff is our number one priority at Friends of Trees
 . We are requiring that all people at our events bring and wear a fabric fa
 ce mask\, respect 6' or more of distance from others not in their own house
 hold\,bringing your own water bottle and any other snacks or beverages you 
