DESCRIPTION:This planting is part of the Tree for All campaign and is in co
 njunction with the City of Beaverton and Clean Water Services. We will be p
 lanting live stakes and bare root shrubs\, restoring the riparian area alon
 g Summer Creek. The ambitious goal of Tree for All is to plant two million 
 trees in the Tualatin River Valley in 20 years. Friends of Trees will provi
 de morning refreshments\, gloves\, tools\, and all necessary guidance. NOTE
 : This area can be very wet\, please wear waterproof boots and dress for th
 e weather. \n\nWe look forward to seeing you out there!  RSVPs are not requ
 ired.  Please contact Andy Meeks at AndyM@FriendsofTrees.org or (503) 595-0
 213 for more information.
