 f Trees for some planting fun with the City of Beaverton -- you'll be plant
 ing native trees\, shrubs\, and wildflowers in the Greenway Neighborhood of
  Beaverton! </b><span>This is the first year in a multi-year planting effor
 t to establish a pollinator hedgerow and native forest habitat in this vita
 l community space. Community support is crucial to the success of this proj
 ect -- thank you for considering signing-up!</span><br></p><p>Please arrive
  by 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts 
