 er volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on t
 heir own and will need to hand us a </span><a href="http://friendsoftrees.o
 rg/youthwaiver"><b><u>youth waiver form</u></b></a><span> signed by their p
 arent/guardian.</span><br></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check out our <a
  href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/"><u><u><u><u><b><u>Volunte
 er FAQ webpage</u></b></u></u></u></u></a>.  Our team is also happy to assi
 st!  Reach us at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><u><u><u><u>
 <b><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></b></u></u></u></u></a> We look forw
 ard to planting together soon!<br></p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event spon
 sor <a href="https://portlandgeneral.com/"><u><u><u>Portland General Electr
