 mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org"><b><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u>
 </b></a> We look forward to planting together soon!</p><p>===<br>Thank you 
 to our event sponsors <a href="https://www.dowl.com/"><u><u><u><u>DOWL</u><
 /u></u></u></a>\, <a href="https://wyldcbd.com/">WYLD</a> &amp\; <a href="h
 ttps://laughingplanet.com/">Laughing Planet</a>.</p><p>===</p><p></p><hr />
 <p></p><p><br>This event is in partnership with Portland Parks and Recreati
 on.</p>
