DESCRIPTION:We will be planting trees and re-mulching previously planted tr
 ees.  We are very excited to continue reforesting the transportation corrid
 or that runs from the Columbia River in the North to the City of Gladstone 
 in the south. Metro\, ODOT\, TriMet\, EMSWCD are partnering this season wit
 h Friends of Trees to increase livability\, habitat and air quality along t
 he I-205 corridor. \n\nPlease arrive around 8:45am to be registered and ass
 igned to a crew. The planting will start promptly at 9:00am. We provide bre
 akfast snacks and hot chocolate/coffee\, as well as gloves\, tools and guid
 ance. Please come dressed for the weather and wearing sturdy shoes and get 
 ready to have fun!\n\nRSVPs are not required. Please contact Andy or Jenny 
 at (503) 595-0213 if you have any questions or need more information. We lo
 ok forward to seeing you out there! \n
