 't be anyone teeing off while we're planting :).&nbsp\; Thank you for for c
 onsidering signing-up -- your support makes it possible for all park users 
 to benefit from a healthy tree canopy!<br><br>Please arrive by 8:45am to si
 gn-in and enjoy some breakfast treats and coffee\, tea\, or hot chocolate. 
 The planting starts at 9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and planting gui
 dance -- all you need to do is show up dressed for the weather wearing stur
 dy shoes or boots\, and be ready to have fun! <br><br><u style="font-weight
 : bold\;">How do I register?</u>&nbsp\;Online registration closes the day b
 efore the event\, but this planting is still open.&nbsp\; Please simply sho
