 uth waiver is required for you to volunteer: <b><a href="http://www.friends
 oftrees.org/youthwaiver">www.friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver</a></b> We ask 
 that youth 15 years and younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please 
 contact Jenny\, Pablo\, and Carey at (503) 595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volu
 nteer@friendsoftrees.org">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a> if you have ques
 tions or need any further information. We look forward to seeing you out th
 ere!
