 lumbia Slough near Colwood Golf Center in NE Portland! </b>Help needed to p
 lant hundreds of native trees and shrubs\, which will help enhance habitat 
 and protect the Columbia Slough!</p><p>Please arrive by 9:45am to sign-in a
 nd be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at 10:00am. We provide 
 gloves\, tools\, and planting guidance\, as well as breakfast snacks and co
 ffee/tea/hot chocolate -- all you need to do is show up dressed for the wea
 ther wearing sturdy shoes or boots\, and be ready to have fun!</p><p>**Ther
 e is a 5 minute walk from the parking area to the planting site - look for 
 our signs to guide you!**</p><p><b>How do I register? </b>Register by filli
 ng out <b><a href="https://www.tfaforms.com/4840511?tfa_26=a0TPa00000soS5c&
 tfa_2189=Colwood%20Natural%20Area%20planting\,%20NE%20Portland&tfa_31=a0VPa
 0000098L7W&tfa_45=Tree%20Planter\,%20%20at%20February%207\,%202026%20at%209
 :45%20am&tfa_2190=2026-02-07&tfa_49=3.25&tfa_886=Portland%20Parks%20and%20R
 ecreation&tfa_51=offsite" target="_blank">this quick form</a></b>.  Groups\
 , families\, and individuals welcome!</p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request
  that youth 15 and under volunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and ol
 der can volunteer on their own and will need to hand us a <b><u><a href="ht
 tp://friendsoftrees.org/youthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><
 u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth waiver form</u></u></u></u></u></u
 ></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> signed by
  their parent/guardian.</p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Pl<u></u>ease check out ou
 r <a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_blank"><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></b></u></u></u>
 </u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.  Our team is also happy to assist! <a
  href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u>
 <u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@fr<u></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u>g</u></b><
 /u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a> / 503-595-0213 We look forw
 ard to working together soon!<br></p><p>===</p><p>Thank you to our event sp
 onsors\, <a href="https://wyldcanna.com/" target="_blank"><u><u>WYLD</u></u
 ></a> &amp\; <a href="http://www.exquisitecrystals.com/" target="_blank">Ex
 quisite Crystals</a>.</p><p>===</p><b><hr /></b><p>This event in partnershi
 p with Portland Parks &amp\; Recreation.<br></p>
