DESCRIPTION:<p>=========</p><p><b>Due to popular interest\, this event is n
 ow <u>full and closed</u></b>.  Please consider the third and final Jackson
  Bottom planting on Sat\, Oct 26th\, or any other open event.  We hope to p
 lant with you soon!</p><p>=========</p><p>Kick off our 24-25 planting seaso
 n by joining the fun at Jackson Bottom Wetlands to plant hundreds of native
  shrubs and trees! Jackson Bottom is a 635-acre wetland complex on the Tual
 atin River that is designated as an Important Bird Area for both migrating 
 and non-migratory species. Thank you for considering signing-up -- your par
 ticipation is crucial for this project's success!<br></p><p>Please arrive b
 y 8:45am to sign-in and be assigned a planting crew. The planting starts at
  9:00am. We provide gloves\, tools\, and planting guidance\, as well as bre
 akfast snacks and coffee/tea/hot chocolate -- all you need to do is show up
  dressed for the weather wearing sturdy shoes or boots\, and be ready to ha
 ve fun!<br></p><p><b>Under age 18?</b> We request that youth 15 and under v
 olunteer with a parent/guardian.  Youth 16 and older can volunteer on their
  own and will need to hand us a <b><u><a href="http://friendsoftrees.org/yo
 uthwaiver" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>youth wai
 ver form</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b> si
 gned by their parent/guardian.<br></p><p><b>Questions?  </b>Please check ou
 t our <b><u><a href="https://friendsoftrees.org/volunteer-faq/" target="_bl
 ank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></u></
 u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our team is also h
 appy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@
 friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b>
 <u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213.  We look forward to planting together soon
 !</p><p>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor <a href="https://epson.com/hi
 llsboro" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u>Epson Portland\, Inc.</u></u></u></u><
 /a></p><p>===</p><hr /><p><b></b></p><p>This event is in partnership with C
 lean Water Services.</p>
