 accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny or Pablo at (503) 595-
 0213 if you have any questions or need more information. We look forward to
  seeing you at Durham city park!<br><br><i>Accessible on Bus Line 76. For m
 ore directions\, visit <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2F
 trimet.org%2F&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1517360467739000&amp\;usg=AFQjCNGSiMe4L3RV
 sIiS9-m0MDBwqbSdVQ" target="_blank">https://trimet.org/</a>.</i><br><br>===
 <br>Thank you to our event sponsors\, <a href="https://www.google.com/url?q
 =https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elemental.com%2F&amp\;sa=D&amp\;ust=1519343741773000&amp
