 ></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.  Our team is also happy 
 to assist!  Reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailto:Volunteer@friendsoftree
 s.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunte
 er@fr<u></u>iendsoftrees.or<u></u>g</u></b></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u>
 </u></u></u></u></u></a> We look forward to working together soon!<br></p><
 p>===<br>Thank you to our event sponsor <a href="https://wyldcanna.com/" ta
 rget="_blank"><u><u><u>Wyld</u></u></u></a>\, <a href="https://portlandgene
 ral.com/">Portland General Electric</a> &amp\; <a href="https://www.honltre
 ecare.com/" target="_blank">Honl Tree Care</a>.</p><p>===</p><hr /><p>This 
 event is in partnership with Portland Parks &amp\; Recreation and <span>7 W
 aters Canoe Family.</span></p>
