DESCRIPTION:<b>Due to popular interest\, this training is now full and clos
 ed.</b> Thank you for your interest!  Please consider training with us next
  Fall\, and attending any of our Salem plantings later this season!\n\nCrew
  Leaders are trained volunteers who are crucial to successful Friends of Tr
 ees' events. They are trained to lead groups of volunteers in proper planti
 ng technique and maintain a fun and educational vibe at our events.\n\nFrie
 nds of Trees is aiming to plant thousands of native trees and shrubs across
  Salem parks and green spaces this year. Help us make those goals a reality
  and register to become a Crew Leader with us! Crew Leaders commit to guidi
 ng small groups of planters at 3-4 Saturday morning plantings\, Nov - April
 .\n\nYou may also contact Jenny or Pablo at (503) 595-0213 if you have any 
 questions or need more information. We hope to see you at the training!\n\n
 ===\nThank you to our event sponsor\, <a href=http://www.tree-source.net/>R
 igert Shade Trees</a>!\n===
