 younger are accompanied by an adult.<br><br>Please contact Jenny\, Pablo\, 
 and Carey at (503) 595-0213 // <a href="mailto:volunteer@friendsoftrees.org
 " target="_blank">volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</a> if you have questions or
  need any further information. We look forward to seeing you out there!<br>
