 k"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>Volunteer FAQ webpage</u></
 u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a></u></b>.  Our te
 am is also happy to assist!  You can reach Cece and Jenny at <a href="mailt
 o:Volunteer@friendsoftrees.org" target="_blank"><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u><u>
 <u><u><u><u><u><b><u>volunteer@friendsoftrees.org</u></b></u></u></u></u></
 u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>\, 503-595-0213. We look forward 
 to planting together soon!</p><p>===</p><p>Thank you to our event sponsor\,
  <a href="https://wyldcanna.com/" target="_blank"><u><u>WYLD</u></u></a>.</
 p><p>===</p><b><hr /></b><p>This event in partnership with Portland Parks &
