DESCRIPTION:<span>=================<br><br><b>Due to popular interest\, thi
 s event is now <u>full and closed</u>.&nbsp\;</b> Please consider any of ou
 r future events that remain open - we hope to plant with you soon!<br><br>=
 ================</span><br><br><b>What about Covid-19?</b>&nbsp\;The safety
